  "title": "Production Supervisor",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform receiving, picking and packing for local &amp; overseas shipments.</li>\n  <li>Schedule production activities</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with Requester/ Planner on stock readiness, deliveries and collections.</li>\n  <li>Work with production &amp; warehouse team to ensure smooth execution of store activities</li>\n  <li>Performs stock cycle counts, labelling and stock arrangement on a regular basis.</li>\n  <li>Ensure good housekeeping in the store and comply with environmental and safety regulations.</li>\n  <li>6-Day Work week</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirement:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Physically fit. Able to carry goods up to 25KG</li>\n  <li>Responsible, team player, proactive and committed worker</li>\n  <li>‘A’ level, acceptable conversational n written English capability (communicate with Indian and Malay colleagues)</li>\n  <li>Forklift License</li>\n  <li>Relevant past experience in production and warehousing</li>\n</ul>",
